PostgreSQL Numeric Types
--------------------------
Data Type	          Storage Size	Range / Precision
smallint / int2	            2 bytes	-32,768 to 32,767
integer / int / int4	    4 bytes	-2,147,483,648 to 2,147,483,647
bigint / int8	            8 bytes	-9,223,372,036,854,775,808 to 9,223,372,036,854,775,807
decimal / numeric	    Variable	User-defined precision, exact values
real / float4	            4 bytes	6 decimal digits precision (approx.)
double precision / float8   8 bytes	15 decimal digits precision (approx.)
serial	                    4 bytes	Auto-incrementing integer (1 to 2,147,483,647)
bigserial	            8 bytes	Auto-incrementing bigint (1 to 9,223,372,036,854,775,807)
